Open Chrome and go to the Extensions page (chrome://extensions/)

Enable the Developer mode by clicking on the toggle switch in the top right corner

Click on the "Load unpacked" button and select the "chat-extension" folder that you created earlier

Your extension should now be loaded in Chrome and you should see its icon in the toolbar.

